350
00:28:42,714 --> 00:28:44,754
Why?
Jesus, Charlie!

351
00:28:45,251 --> 00:28:47,193
Shut up! Read your book.

352
00:29:03,439 --> 00:29:06,341
Have you ever heard of Larry Lacker?
Who?

353
00:29:06,542 --> 00:29:10,503
My dad. He's like the greatest
