00:30:16,288 --> 00:30:17,979
Hello?

363
00:30:23,963 --> 00:30:25,970
Bessie?

364
00:30:30,004 --> 00:30:31,083
Lee?

365
00:30:40,083 --> 00:30:42,025
Oh!

366
00:30:44,689 --> 00:30:47,885
