399
00:33:40,421 --> 00:33:43,104
Give me a hug!
Oh!

400
00:33:43,324 --> 00:33:46,969
Oh, give me a real hug!
I won't break.

401
00:33:49,399 --> 00:33:51,766
Oh, oh, Jesus, sweet Jesus!

402
00:34:01,110 --> 00:34:03,118
Oh! Oh, that's much better.

