406
00:34:12,156 --> 00:34:15,320
But this is just
a lovely canister.

407
00:34:15,528 --> 00:34:18,562
Oh, I'm missing my program.

408
00:34:18,765 --> 00:34:20,620
Oh!

409
00:34:20,767 --> 00:34:23,801
Yeah, you go watch
your program.

410
00:34:24,405 --> 00:34:26,478
